<p>How do I exclude dependencies form my target platform configuration and my repo using a custom filter, here by custom filter, I mean something like this :</p>  <pre><code>    &lt;filter&gt;         &lt;?&gt;(&amp;(osgi.ee=JavaSE)(version=1.6))&lt;/?&gt;         &lt;removeAll /&gt;      &lt;/filter&gt; </code></pre>  <p>I've looked here <a href="https://wiki.eclipse.org/Tycho/Target_Platform" rel="nofollow">Tycho Doc</a> but it seems that you can filter dependencies by id, verionRange but not using osgi filter. If not is there any other mean to apply this filter?</p>